Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:13.29,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}好害怕 暗地里的自己将现实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:18.98,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}映照而出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:24.36,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}指尖描绘着相同的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:29.04,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}这里一定是脆弱的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.04,0:22:31.73,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}追逐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.73,0:22:36.09,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}梦里的我在蓝天高高飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.09,0:22:42.45,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}无论肉体有多不安 都能够挣脱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.45,0:22:46.78,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}守护那点点的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.78,0:22:48.98,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}蔓延我心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.99,0:22:50.99,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}察觉到 软弱的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:53.03,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}只要有你在
